h-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-theme-post-featured-image elementor-widget-image" data-id="ee60029" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="theme-post-featured-image.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"> <img width="600" height="800" src="https://americasbesthearing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/shyanne-abbott-e1760785035660.webp" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-2000" alt="Woman with brown hair wearing glasses and cream sweater with lace collar" srcset="https://americasbesthearing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/shyanne-abbott-e1760785035660.webp 600w, https://americasbesthearing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/shyanne-abbott-e1760785035660-225x300.webp 225w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-0a3ed6d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="0a3ed6d" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-31c12d5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="31c12d5" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Location: <span>Roseville, MN</span></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9736eea elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="9736eea" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p>Shyanne Abbott is a licensed Hearing Instrument Specialist Trainee with a strong passion for helping people improve their quality of life through better hearing. She is skilled in evaluating hearing needs, fitting and programming devices, and providing patient-centered care that enhances communication and confidence.</p><p>Hearing healthcare runs in Shyanne’s family. Her grandparents owned a hearing aid center, and several of her relatives including her mother, aunts, and grandparents worked as hearing instrument specialists or in hearing aid manufacturing. Inspired by their legacy, she chose to follow the same path.</p><p>Shyanne focuses on patient care and guiding patients through their hearing journey. She takes pride in delivering personalized solutions that help individuals reconnect with the world around them.</p><p>Outside of work, Shyanne enjoys spending time with her family, building Lego sets with her significant other, and getting lost in a good book. She also loves to travel, hike, and explore the outdoors.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b9cf67b e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="b9cf67b" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6f828f5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-theme-post-content" data-id="6f828f5" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="theme-post-content.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="1932" class="elementor elementor-1932" data-elementor-post-type="audiologist"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-4d0902d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent" data-id="4d0902d" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-2cf257b elementor-grid-1 elementor-grid-tablet-1 elementor-grid-mobile-1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-loop-grid" data-id="2cf257b" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-settings="{&quot;template_id&quot;:&quot;200&quot;,&quot;columns&quot;:1,&quot;columns_tablet&quot;:1,&quot;_skin&quot;:&quot;post&quot;,&quot;columns_mobile&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;edit_handle_selector&quot;:&quot;[data-elementor-type=\&quot;loop-item\&quot;]&quot;,&quot;row_gap&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;s